The paper discusses the calibration of sensors for environment perception, which is a key component of autonomous systems. This topic is closely related to robotics (cs.RO), computer vision (cs.CV), and control systems (cs.SY). The paper also mentions the use of features in the environment for calibration, which is a common technique in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Therefore, these five categories are the most likely ones for this paper.
